{"tid":2164481,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得紅黃藍幼稚園性侵幼童事件","createTime":"2020-08-19T08:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T03:52:51.000Z","uid":191453,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"886a0baa04fe75d525e8e5cef469a63f5e07eb7a","tid":2164481,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"當年睇到完全覺得大陸CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然成功用幼稚園做到禁室培慾試點<br />\n最後拉9曬啲話有性侵嘅家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />件事好似勁快淡出大眾視野<br />\n全面一國一制後販賣幼女不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝1/3/5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-620b9cd1d603ca877e09136007b29198_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-620b9cd1d603ca877e09136007b29198_hd.jpg&h=41846695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FcWaz6r_2Gc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFcWaz6r_2Gc&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=f93d424d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FcWaz6r_2Gc</a>"},{"pid":"acac37a942b2c4dcc4b7af1efa159943737f62cb","tid":2164481,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0dk3QhlQ5Ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0dk3QhlQ5Ug&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=4012bed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0dk3QhlQ5Ug</a><br />\n為北京警方點贊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友反串Lv Max"},{"pid":"068eef29278e6df2265412c81848b7e9cc2dabce","tid":2164481,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"孩子躺下比劃了一下。家長當時就發現了不對。就試探的問了一下，&ldquo;檢查的時候脫衣服了嗎？&rdquo;童童說<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">&ldquo;小朋友們光溜溜，叔叔也光溜溜&rdquo;。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽媽覺得童童只有3歲，有可能表達出現誤差，就把爸爸叫來，讓童童把爸爸當做醫生叔叔，情景再現。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">結果孩子不僅讓爸爸脫了上衣，還讓他脫了褲子。</span></span></strong>而最大的災難是，當媽媽問&ldquo;怎麼檢查身體的？&rdquo;之後，她眼淚一下就下來了。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>只有3歲的孩子，把他這個年紀最不應該知道的一整套床上動作都模仿了一遍。</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來，媽媽推測，當時孩子們應該是在圍觀醫生叔叔猥褻別的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n後來，童童家長聯繫了別的家長，陸續有8個孩子家長確認在孩子身上找到了針眼兒。"},{"pid":"eba8a05c50fdee202b77fa564aaa4f8057ad42f5","tid":2164481,"uid":327483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"之後大陸封鎖左單新聞"},{"pid":"6d33233ceb96fdcb0e2137483f460407f505307c","tid":2164481,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eba8a05c50fdee202b77fa564aaa4f8057ad42f5","tid":2164481,"uid":327483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"之後大陸封鎖左單新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vAKG2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vAKG2X.jpg&h=2579803f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n&quot;微博，贴吧，一评论就被删，只能在这看了&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066222553e2374296cb672b1cd5074d9bed56b47","tid":2164481,"uid":191453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNt0ZRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNt0ZRO.jpg&h=dc39c3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小粉紅邏輯: 畀啲時間黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢之後會好㗎啦"},{"pid